OL,3,GUK weather for today and tomorrow
OL,4,
OL,5,CToday:FDry with sunny spells for many.
OL,6,FFurther showers are likely to affect
OL,7,Fwindward coasts at first, with a few
OL,8,Fscattered showers developing inland
OL,9,Facross England and Wales, although not
OL,10,Fas heavy as on Thursday. Feeling less
OL,11,Fcold than recent days.
OL,12,
OL,13,CTonight:FA few showers will drift
OL,14,Fsouthwards, but many areas dry with
OL,15,Fclear spells. Cloud and rain arriving
OL,16,Facross the far west towards dawn. A
OL,17,Fpatchy frost possible in the
OL,18,Fcountryside.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
OL,24,ANext Page  BWeather  CReg News  FReg TV
