OL,3,GUK weather for today and tomorrow
OL,4,
OL,5,CSaturday:FA sunny morning for most.
OL,6,FCloud and rain across the far west
OL,7,Fwill slowly move eastwards as the day
OL,8,Fprogresses, reaching the far east by
OL,9,Flate evening. Still chilly.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
